author: Codi Wilson, CP24.com
title: Woman killed in early morning Etobicoke crash
text:
Toronto police say a 41-year-old woman has died after a crash in Etobicoke early this morning.
The collision occurred near Kipling Avenue and Burnhamthorpe Road.
Police say the victim was a passenger in the vehicle and the male driver remains in hospital in serious condition.
There is no word on whether charges will be laid.
